<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="low-adv">low <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ləʊ/    美 /loʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>低；低声地；低水平地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The planes flew very low.  
飞机飞得很低。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 6</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They talked low so as not to be heard. 
他们低声交谈以免被他人听到。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She bought it low. 
这东西她买得便宜。</p></div></div>